---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Reveal from '../components/react/Reveal';
import SocialButtons from '../components/react/SocialButtons';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="About | Aryan">
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-container px-6">
      <Reveal client:visible>
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white/50">About</p>
          <h1 class="mt-4 font-heading text-4xl">Building Products at the intersection of Security and Systems</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-white/70">
            Hi, I’m Aryan. I study computer science and spend most of my time working on problems that sit somewhere
            between engineering, product, and strategy. I’m interested in how complex technical systems actually work,
            from security infrastructure to large online platforms, and how those systems can be turned into tools or
            products people can use.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-white/70">
            When I work on projects, I tend to think both like a builder and like a systems analyst. I like breaking
            down messy problems, figuring out what the real constraint is, and then building something practical around
            it. A lot of my work ends up in areas like cybersecurity, data privacy, and internet governance, where
            technical design decisions often have wider policy or societal effects.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-white/70">
            What draws me most is making opaque systems easier to understand and interact with. This can mean building
            better tooling, designing clearer interfaces, or approaching the problem from a product perspective.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <SocialButtons size="md" showLetterboxd />
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <Reveal client:visible>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">Focus Areas</h2>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/70">
              <li>Security and privacy product design</li>
              <li>Cybersecurity systems and infrastructure</li>
              <li>Platform governance and digital policy</li>
              <li>Technical strategy and system design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </Reveal>
        <Reveal client:visible>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">Experience Highlights</h2>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/70">
              <li>
                Cybersecurity Intern at Alcon Cyber Security, where I worked on security assessments, threat analysis,
                and practical exposure to vulnerability identification and remediation.
              </li>
              <li>
                Researched how digital policy and regulatory decisions affect network-level filtering and access to
                information.
              </li>
              <li>
                Contributed to open-source privacy-focused telemetry tools designed to reduce unnecessary data
                collection.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </Reveal>
      </div>

      <Reveal client:visible>
        <div class="mt-12">
          <a
            href={`${base}resume.pdf`}
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border border-white/20 px-6 py-3 text-sm text-white/80 transition hover:text-white"
          >
            [Download resume (PDF)]
          </a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
